<Speech gate:gateId="254387" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="250083" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="255822" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="252284" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="251518" majorType="speaker">Ιωάννης Δριβελέγκας</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Να ακούσω το προσωπικό σας, κύριε Νταβλούρο. 
