<Speech gate:gateId="254619" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="250315" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="255915" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="252377" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="251611" majorType="speaker">Ιωάννης Δραγασάκης</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Ευχαριστούμε κι εμείς. 
