<Speech gate:gateId="255112" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="250808" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="256095" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="252557" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="251791" majorType="speaker">Χρήστος Μαρκογιαννάκης</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Παρακαλώ, κυρία Κωνσταντοπούλου.</Speech></Speech>
<Speech gate:gateId="255113" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="253605" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="250809" majorType="speaker">ΖΩΗ ΚΩΝΣΤΑΝΤΟΠΟΥΛΟΥ</Parlmember>:</SpeechStart> Μα είναι ψέματα αυτά που λέει!</Speech>
<Speech gate:gateId="255114" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="250810" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="256096" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="252558" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="251792" majorType="speaker">Χρήστος Μαρκογιαννάκης</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Λέμε και ψέματα καμμία φορά. Τι να κάνουμε;</Speech></Speech>
